Have you tried our deep cleaning brush soap? This soap is so GOOD! 
Deep cleans brushes and sponges leaving them smelling of mango & bergamot tea while the Rose Quartz Crystal infuses love and beauty back into your tools! 

Pro Tip: Did you know it’s important to wash your brushes with a soap vs liquid cleansers as the liquids can dry out and break off bristles? It’s especially important to use soap’s for synthetic brushes as the liquids will stiffen and tweak the bristles. 

This soap is included in a few of our value bundles that will expire end of month 🤍
